
= SDL_GetWindowFlags =
Use this function to get the window flags.


== Syntax ==
```c++
Uint32 SDL_GetWindowFlags(SDL_Window* window)
```

== Function Parameters ==
{|
|'''window'''
|the window to query
|}

== Return Value ==
Returns a mask of the [[SDL_WindowFlags]] associated with '''window'''; see [[#Remarks|Remarks]] for details.

